==I derman==

===At Wejɛud (At Wejaoud)===

At Wejɛud d'a drum a meqran n taddart yesɛa azal n carit (30) ye xxamen, a drum aki yebḍa ɣef krad (3) nneqmat (nom de famille) deg tira Ta fransist garasen '''Adjed''', '''Djaouani''' akk d '''Djaou'''.

ass aki ta wacult '''Adjed''' d nutni id yegran aṭṭas deg we drum acku tawacult '''Djaou''' udren akk ɣer [[Taddart: Taqriett|Tqeriett]] ma d '''Djaouani''' akk d '''Adjed''' aṭṭas daɣen ig udren ɣer [[Taddart: Taqriett|Tqeriett]], dacu aṭṭas ig qqimen deg taddart.

===At Ḥemmic (fr:At Hemmiche)===

At Ḥemmic d'a drum wis ssin meqren deg taddart yesɛa azal n warim (20) ye xxamen, a drum aki yebḍa ɣef sin nneqmat deg tira Ta fransist garasen ad naf '''Hamadi''' akk d '''Hamlaoui''', adrum n At Musa ('''mouzaoui''') d'a drum ig zedwen ɣersen, ass aki at ḥemmic akk d w'at musa uɣalen d yiwen we drum.

===At Belɛid (fr:At Belaaid)===

At Belɛid d'adrum ig sɛan azal n mraw semmus (15) ye xxamen, daɣen yebḍa ɣef krad nneqmat grasen ad naf '''Belazouz''', '''Aouchiche''' akk d '''Belbahi'''. At Weḥmaduc d'a drum i win mi ssawalen '''sebḥi''', izdew ɣer we drum n at belɛid, ass aki i uqqus (4) d'yiwen we drum.

===At Musa (At Moussa)===

Adrum n'At Musa d win ittawin isem n '''mouzaoui''', deg taddart llan azal n mraw (10) ye xxamen

